## Practical Recommendation

Build `v0.9.9` around this sentence:

**SessionFS v0.9.9 manages canonical project rules and captures the full instruction provenance that shaped each session.**

That is the smallest strong version of the product idea.

It is enough to be differentiated, useful, and shippable without overreaching into a full multi-tool behavior platform in one release.
